  <title translate="true">Saving Your Searches</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Saving Your Searches</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">You can save your search settings so that you can re-use them again. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Press the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Save</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> button to save the current configuration. You will be asked for a name that will be displayed in the list of saved searches.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">To load a search, press the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Load</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> button and select a saved search from the list.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="multiline_search_saved_searches.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
  </body>
